flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Admin/Librarian opens Detailed Reports]
    B --> C{Authorized role?}
    C -->|No| C1[Access denied] --> Z([End])
    C -->|Yes| D[Select report type: Books/Borrows/Fines/Lost-Damaged]
    D --> E[Select time range Day/Week/Month/Quarter/Year]
    E --> F[System queries and aggregates report data]
    F --> G[Render charts and tables]
    G --> H{Export CSV?}
    H -->|No| Z
    H -->|Yes| I[Generate and download CSV]
    I --> Z([End])
